data.description: Welcome home to this absolutely beautiful, open concept, better than new home! This home built in 2019 is located in a pristine, 24/7 Guarded, golf course, club house, resort style community. This home features soaring ceilings, solid oak flooring and large tile throughout. The kitchen has a huge island, granite countertops stainless steel appliances and plenty of room for all your kitchen needs. The primary suite is king bed sized with enough room for seating , the attached primary bath has large tile flooring , dual sinks, soaking tub, glass enclosed shower with sitting bench and water closet. This home has wide hallways ,upgraded lighting and a water filter/softener . The garage has extra room for tandem golf cart parking. There's tons of natural light in every room. The community is pristine with everything you can think of , hugeclubhouse with a bar and 2 restaurants , nature trails, ponds, Pickle ball/tennis courts, softball, social activities and the preferred method of transportation is golf carts (of course) RV/Camper parking and so much more. This home has fresh paint and is move in ready! Schedule your easy showing today!
